descriptionMarkdown:
🌟 Hey everyone, I’m Cloudiboy! 🌟

Today I want to share with you my Legendary Smelting setup for copper and iron! 🔥⛓️
One special highlight of this build is the integrated light system on the recyclers – it shows you at a glance which ones are currently working and which ones are idle. 💡🔄 Super handy to keep track of everything!

🔋 The system is fueled by two full green belts each (4 Stacks high), for both iron and copper. Please make sure to keep that in mind! ⚙️⚡

👉 Important: To ensure a clean output, your mining drills must use quality modules! 🚀 I built this entire system around legendary quality modules. It will still work with lower quality modules since I controle the input to the recyclers.
If you use lower-quality modules, you may need to adjust the inserters on the recyclers, because lower quality ores produce more lower material at once. 🔧🎯 Otherwise, the flow might not stay clean!

 📈🔬It is highly recommended to use legendary mining drills and to have high productivity research.

🎁 And now? I hope some of you will find this setup useful – or at least inspiring! 😄 Maybe it’ll help you fine-tune your own designs! 🚀

Best wishes & have fun,
Your Cloudiboy 👋🙂
title: Cloudiboy's Legendary Copper/Iron Smelting
